        "liquid": "<section class=\"elixara-reviews\">\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-reviews-head\">\n    <p>Real Results</p>\n    <h2>Women are getting their confidence back</h2>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-reviews-track\">\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S4c7470a50d084c499fac5328375d66a6g.avif?v=1778879618\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“I saw less hair fall.”</h3>\n      <p>After a few weeks, my brush had noticeably less hair. I finally feel hopeful again.</p>\n      <span>— Amanda, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/Sff73f76a035449af95a4c862a9e25587i.avif?v=1778879594\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“My hair feels fuller.”</h3>\n      <p>I was skeptical, but my roots look stronger and my hair feels thicker.</p>\n      <span>— Jessica, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S352ae5c1c6404706bcce5a60c49df6cct.avif?v=1778879580\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“It actually works.”</h3>\n      <p>I noticed baby hairs around my hairline. That was the moment I believed it.</p>\n      <span>— Lauren, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S8c1199a3498944c9a028a1ed85a7a396c.avif?v=1778879565\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“I feel confident again.”</h3>\n      <p>I stopped hiding my hair in photos. That alone makes it worth it.</p>\n      <span>— Emily, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/Sbf5c1cd2b5c84000af70493b76f2d13f2_2742855d-fd0b-4c65-91e3-45d62262284f.avif?v=1778879542\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“My ponytail looks thicker.”</h3>\n      <p>My hair feels stronger and less fragile when I brush it.</p>\n      <span>— Rachel, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S2948ed64857744d2bf25008621603ab9p_d5c4907d-6bcf-40a9-bc17-a3b4db4791d7.avif?v=1778879521\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“Wish I ordered sooner.”</h3>\n      <p>I kept waiting, but I’m so glad I finally tried it.</p>\n      <span>— Nicole, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S91852db5cba648d19205124f1422aec3o.avif?v=1778879507\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“So easy to use.”</h3>\n      <p>I apply it at night and forget about it. Super simple routine.</p>\n      <span>— Megan, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/Sdc3f7a8d208d450f8c8a0989d85b836et.avif?v=1778879491\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“My scalp feels healthier.”</h3>\n      <p>It doesn’t feel greasy, and my hair feels fresher at the roots.</p>\n      <span>— Sarah, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/Se51ad6e3a31947a1a78a5cbefd3e020b9.avif?v=1778879455\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“Less shedding fast.”</h3>\n      <p>I noticed fewer strands in the shower during the first weeks.</p>\n      <span>— Chloe, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"review-card\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S35ce60888a7c4782961aad320a52d684G_b85a1f14-ec08-4887-82cf-3d65a5418a23.avif?v=1778879439\">\n      <div>★★★★★</div>\n      <h3>“Beautiful results.”</h3>\n      <p>My hair looks healthier, shinier, and easier to style.</p>\n      <span>— Olivia, verified buyer</span>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<style>\n\n.elixara-reviews{\n  width:100vw;\n  margin-left:calc(50% - 50vw);\n  margin-right:calc(50% - 50vw);\n\n  background:#ffffff;\n\n  padding:40px 0;\n\n  overflow:hidden;\n\n  border-top:1px solid rgba(6,59,42,.08);\n  border-bottom:1px solid rgba(6,59,42,.08);\n}\n\n.elixara-reviews-head{\n  text-align:center;\n  padding:0 16px;\n  margin-bottom:26px;\n}\n\n.elixara-reviews-head p{\n  color:#b88722;\n  font-weight:900;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  letter-spacing:1.5px;\n  margin:0 0 8px;\n  font-size:13px;\n}\n\n.elixara-reviews-head h2{\n  color:#063b2a;\n  font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,54px);\n  line-height:1;\n  margin:0;\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n/* TRACK */\n\n.elixara-reviews-track{\n  display:flex;\n  gap:16px;\n\n  overflow-x:auto;\n\n  scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n\n  padding:0 16px 8px;\n\n  -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n\n  scrollbar-width:none;\n}\n\n.elixara-reviews-track::-webkit-scrollbar{\n  display:none;\n}\n\n/* CARD */\n\n.review-card{\n  flex:0 0 300px;\n\n  scroll-snap-align:center;\n\n  background:#ffffff;\n\n  border-radius:22px;\n\n  padding:14px;\n\n  border:1px solid rgba(6,59,42,.08);\n\n  box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.04);\n}\n\n.review-card img{\n  width:100%;\n  height:230px;\n  object-fit:cover;\n  border-radius:18px;\n  display:block;\n  margin-bottom:12px;\n}\n\n.review-card div{\n  color:#00b67a;\n  font-size:15px;\n  letter-spacing:1px;\n  margin-bottom:8px;\n}\n\n.review-card h3{\n  color:#063b2a;\n  font-size:20px;\n  margin:0 0 8px;\n  line-height:1.1;\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n.review-card p{\n  color:#4d6257;\n  font-size:14px;\n  line-height:1.45;\n  margin:0 0 12px;\n}\n\n.review-card span{\n  color:#063b2a;\n  font-size:13px;\n  font-weight:800;\n}\n\n/* MOBILE */\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n\n  .elixara-reviews{\n    padding:34px 0;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-reviews-track{\n    padding:0 14px 6px;\n  }\n\n  .review-card{\n    flex-basis:260px;\n    border-radius:20px;\n  }\n\n  .review-card img{\n    height:200px;\n    border-radius:16px;\n  }\n\n  .review-card h3{\n    font-size:18px;\n  }\n\n}\n\n</style>",
