            "liquid": "<section class=\"elixara-product-summary\">\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-rating-line\">\n    <span class=\"stars\">★★★★★</span>\n    <span>Rated 4.8/5 — 1,281 reviews</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <h1>Elixara™</h1>\n\n  <h2>\n    The daily ritual for fuller, healthier hair\n  </h2>\n\n  <ul class=\"elixara-checklist\">\n\n    <li>\n      Visibly reduces hair fall from the first weeks\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n      Supports stronger, fuller-looking hair naturally\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n      Promotes healthier roots and scalp balance\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n      Zero harsh chemicals — gentle on sensitive scalps\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n      <strong>Only a few minutes a day</strong>\n    </li>\n\n    <li>\n      Natural alternative to expensive hair treatments\n    </li>\n\n  </ul>\n\n</section>\n\n<style>\n\n.elixara-product-summary{\n  background:#ffffff;\n  padding:12px 0 16px;\n  margin:0;\n  color:#2d1d16;\n}\n\n/* RATING */\n\n.elixara-rating-line{\n  display:flex;\n  align-items:center;\n  gap:8px;\n\n  font-size:14px;\n\n  color:#8d7f72;\n\n  margin-bottom:14px;\n\n  line-height:1.2;\n}\n\n/* TRUSTPILOT GREEN */\n\n.elixara-rating-line .stars{\n  color:#00b67a;\n\n  letter-spacing:1px;\n\n  font-size:17px;\n\n  line-height:1;\n\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n/* TITLE */\n\n.elixara-product-summary h1{\n  font-family:Georgia,serif;\n\n  font-size:clamp(30px,4vw,48px);\n\n  line-height:1;\n\n  color:#2d1d16;\n\n  margin:0 0 8px;\n\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n/* SUBTITLE */\n\n.elixara-product-summary h2{\n  font-family:Georgia,serif;\n\n  font-style:italic;\n\n  font-size:clamp(18px,2.5vw,28px);\n\n  line-height:1.2;\n\n  color:#b88722;\n\n  margin:0 0 18px;\n\n  font-weight:800;\n}\n\n/* LIST */\n\n.elixara-checklist{\n  list-style:none;\n\n  padding:0;\n\n  margin:0;\n\n  display:flex;\n\n  flex-direction:column;\n\n  gap:12px;\n}\n\n.elixara-checklist li{\n  position:relative;\n\n  padding-left:30px;\n\n  font-size:clamp(15px,2vw,20px);\n\n  line-height:1.45;\n\n  color:#2d1d16;\n\n  font-weight:500;\n}\n\n/* CHECK */\n\n.elixara-checklist li::before{\n  content:\"✓\";\n\n  position:absolute;\n\n  left:0;\n\n  top:0;\n\n  color:#b88722;\n\n  font-size:18px;\n\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n.elixara-checklist strong{\n  font-weight:900;\n}\n\n/* MOBILE */\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n\n  .elixara-product-summary{\n    padding:10px 0 14px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-rating-line{\n    font-size:13px;\n    margin-bottom:12px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-rating-line .stars{\n    font-size:16px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-product-summary h1{\n    font-size:34px;\n    margin-bottom:7px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-product-summary h2{\n    font-size:21px;\n    margin-bottom:16px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-checklist{\n    gap:10px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-checklist li{\n    padding-left:28px;\n    font-size:16px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-checklist li::before{\n    font-size:17px;\n  }\n\n}\n\n</style>"
