        "liquid": "<section class=\"elixara-routine\">\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-title\">\n    <p>HOW TO USE</p>\n    <h2>Simple to use,<br><span>powerful results</span></h2>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-steps\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/ChatGPT_Image_May_14_2026_06_23_20_PM.png?v=1778775864\" alt=\"Elixara Step 1\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/ChatGPT_Image_May_14_2026_06_25_12_PM.png?v=1778775957\" alt=\"Elixara Step 2\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/ChatGPT_Image_May_14_2026_06_27_08_PM.png?v=1778776047\" alt=\"Elixara Step 3\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/ChatGPT_Image_May_14_2026_06_28_52_PM.png?v=1778776169\" alt=\"Elixara Step 4\">\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-stats\">\n    <div><strong>87%</strong><span>Less hair fall after 1 month</span></div>\n    <div><strong>4-6</strong><span>Weeks to notice visible results</span></div>\n    <div><strong>5 months</strong><span>Recommended full routine</span></div>\n    <div><strong>+2400</strong><span>Happy customers worldwide</span></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-title testimonials-title\">\n    <p>REVIEWS</p>\n    <h2>They tried it,<br><span>they loved it</span></h2>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"elixara-reviews\">\n\n    <div class=\"elixara-review-card\">\n      <img class=\"review-photo\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S35ce60888a7c4782961aad320a52d684G.avif?v=1778776535\" alt=\"Emily R.\">\n      <div class=\"review-content\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"After post-partum shedding, I started the full routine. After 8 weeks, my hair looked fuller and my roots felt stronger.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-name\">\n          <strong>Emily R.</strong>\n          <span>Miami, USA</span>\n          <em>✓ Verified Purchase</em>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"elixara-review-card\">\n      <img class=\"review-photo\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/S2948ed64857744d2bf25008621603ab9p.avif?v=1778776545\" alt=\"Jessica M.\">\n      <div class=\"review-content\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"In 6 weeks, my hair started looking thicker and healthier. The serum is small, but very concentrated.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-name\">\n          <strong>Jessica M.</strong>\n          <span>Los Angeles, USA</span>\n          <em>✓ Verified Purchase</em>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"elixara-review-card\">\n      <img class=\"review-photo\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1039/0962/2090/files/Sbf5c1cd2b5c84000af70493b76f2d13f2.avif?v=1778776553\" alt=\"Mark T.\">\n      <div class=\"review-content\">\n        <div class=\"stars\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"review-text\">\"My thinning areas used to bother me a lot. After 3 months, my hair looks stronger, denser, and easier to style.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"review-name\">\n          <strong>Mark T.</strong>\n          <span>New York, USA</span>\n          <em>✓ Verified Purchase</em>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n</section>\n\n<style>\n.elixara-routine{\n  background:#f4f0e7;\n  padding:70px 20px;\n  overflow:hidden;\n}\n\n.elixara-title{\n  text-align:center;\n  margin-bottom:45px;\n}\n\n.elixara-title p{\n  color:#c8ab63;\n  letter-spacing:7px;\n  font-size:14px;\n  margin:0 0 18px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n}\n\n.elixara-title h2{\n  font-family:serif;\n  font-size:clamp(38px,6vw,68px);\n  line-height:1.05;\n  font-weight:400;\n  color:#111;\n  margin:0;\n}\n\n.elixara-title h2 span{\n  color:#2f6b46;\n  font-style:italic;\n}\n\n.elixara-steps{\n  max-width:1200px;\n  margin:0 auto 70px;\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);\n  gap:22px;\n}\n\n.elixara-steps img{\n  width:100%;\n  aspect-ratio:1/1;\n  object-fit:cover;\n  display:block;\n  border-radius:28px;\n  box-shadow:0 12px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\n}\n\n.elixara-stats{\n  background:#0c2b1b;\n  max-width:1200px;\n  margin:0 auto 80px;\n  padding:55px 35px;\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);\n  gap:25px;\n  text-align:center;\n}\n\n.elixara-stats div{\n  border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);\n  padding:0 18px;\n}\n\n.elixara-stats div:last-child{\n  border-right:none;\n}\n\n.elixara-stats strong{\n  display:block;\n  color:#d6b76a;\n  font-family:serif;\n  font-size:clamp(42px,5vw,70px);\n  font-weight:400;\n  line-height:1;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n}\n\n.elixara-stats span{\n  display:block;\n  color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  letter-spacing:5px;\n  font-size:13px;\n  line-height:1.4;\n}\n\n.testimonials-title{\n  margin-top:20px;\n}\n\n.elixara-reviews{\n  max-width:1150px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n  display:grid;\n  grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);\n  gap:28px;\n}\n\n.elixara-review-card{\n  background:#fff;\n  border-radius:34px;\n  overflow:hidden;\n  box-shadow:0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\n}\n\n.review-photo{\n  width:100%;\n  aspect-ratio:1/1;\n  object-fit:cover;\n  display:block;\n}\n\n.review-content{\n  padding:32px;\n}\n\n.stars{\n  color:#c8ab63;\n  font-size:22px;\n  letter-spacing:3px;\n  margin-bottom:20px;\n}\n\n.review-text{\n  font-family:serif;\n  font-style:italic;\n  font-size:22px;\n  line-height:1.65;\n  color:#111;\n  margin:0 0 28px;\n}\n\n.review-name strong{\n  display:block;\n  font-size:17px;\n  letter-spacing:3px;\n  color:#111;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n}\n\n.review-name span{\n  display:block;\n  font-size:15px;\n  color:#777;\n  margin-top:5px;\n}\n\n.review-name em{\n  display:block;\n  margin-top:9px;\n  color:#2f6b46;\n  font-style:normal;\n  font-size:13px;\n  letter-spacing:2px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n}\n\n@media screen and (max-width:768px){\n\n  .elixara-routine{\n    padding:55px 0;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-title{\n    padding:0 20px;\n    margin-bottom:35px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-title p{\n    font-size:12px;\n    letter-spacing:6px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-title h2{\n    font-size:40px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-steps{\n    display:flex;\n    overflow-x:auto;\n    gap:16px;\n    padding:0 20px 16px;\n    margin-bottom:55px;\n    scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-steps img{\n    min-width:72%;\n    max-width:72%;\n    aspect-ratio:1/1;\n    object-fit:cover;\n    flex-shrink:0;\n    scroll-snap-align:center;\n    border-radius:24px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-steps::-webkit-scrollbar{\n    display:none;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-stats{\n    display:flex;\n    overflow-x:auto;\n    gap:18px;\n    margin:35px 0 65px;\n    padding:42px 20px;\n    scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-stats div{\n    min-width:70%;\n    flex-shrink:0;\n    scroll-snap-align:center;\n    border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);\n    padding:0 25px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-stats::-webkit-scrollbar{\n    display:none;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-stats strong{\n    font-size:52px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-stats span{\n    font-size:11px;\n    letter-spacing:4px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-reviews{\n    display:flex;\n    overflow-x:auto;\n    gap:18px;\n    padding:0 20px 16px;\n    scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-review-card{\n    min-width:82%;\n    max-width:82%;\n    flex-shrink:0;\n    scroll-snap-align:center;\n    border-radius:30px;\n  }\n\n  .elixara-reviews::-webkit-scrollbar{\n    display:none;\n  }\n\n  .review-content{\n    padding:26px;\n  }\n\n  .review-text{\n    font-size:20px;\n    line-height:1.6;\n  }\n\n  .review-name strong{\n    font-size:15px;\n    letter-spacing:2px;\n  }\n\n  .review-name span{\n    font-size:14px;\n  }\n\n  .review-name em{\n    font-size:12px;\n    letter-spacing:1.5px;\n  }\n}\n</style>",
